- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is a possible category as sparse coding has many applications in image processing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the implementation of the algorithm in neural circuits. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possible category as the paper discusses the trade-off between sparsity and reconstruction error in sparse coding.
